027  public ProductPriceSearchProjection<ProductSearchVariantProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> price(
028      Currency currency, String country, String customerGroupId, String channelId,
029      OffsetDateTime date) {
030    ProductPriceSearchProjection<ProductSearchVariantProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> projection = new ProductPriceSearchProjection<>(this, getRoot());    
031    getFields().put("price", projection);
032    getInputArguments().computeIfAbsent("price", k -> new ArrayList<>());                      
033    InputArgument currencyArg = new InputArgument("currency", currency);
034    getInputArguments().get("price").add(currencyArg);
035    InputArgument countryArg = new InputArgument("country", country);
036    getInputArguments().get("price").add(countryArg);
037    InputArgument customerGroupIdArg = new InputArgument("customerGroupId", customerGroupId);
038    getInputArguments().get("price").add(customerGroupIdArg);
039    InputArgument channelIdArg = new InputArgument("channelId", channelId);
040    getInputArguments().get("price").add(channelIdArg);
041    InputArgument dateArg = new InputArgument("date", date);
042    getInputArguments().get("price").add(dateArg);
043    return projection;
044  }
